videos.headline: Aliyah Boston powers through her defender for the finish
videos.description: Aliyah Boston backs her defender down in the post for an easy layup for the Gamecocks.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aliyah Boston powers through her defender for the finish) 2023/03/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina's Brea Beal gets the and-1 transition layup to fall
videos.description: Brea Beal runs out on a fast break, gets her defender in the air with a pump fake and gets the layup to fall for the and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (South Carolina's Brea Beal gets the and-1 transition layup to fall) 2023/03/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aliyah Boston fights through multiple defenders under the rim
videos.description: Aliyah Boston shrugs off a double team in the paint to get the bucket for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aliyah Boston fights through multiple defenders under the rim) 2023/03/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zia Cooke channels her inner Dirk for South Carolina
videos.description: Zia Cooke knocks down a tough fallaway jumper off one leg to build South Carolina's lead vs. Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Zia Cooke channels her inner Dirk for South Carolina) 2023/03/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Madison Scott gets the and-1 layup to fall
videos.description: Madison Scott drives through the lane and fights through contact to get the and-1 bucket.

videos.headline: Boston reacts to breaking Gamecocks' rebound record
videos.description: Following a commanding win over the Rebels, Aliyah Boston explains why it's "something special" to become South Carolina's career leader in rebounds.

videos.headline: Gamecocks advance to championship in dominant fashion
videos.description: Top-ranked South Carolina eliminates 4-seed Ole Miss in the semifinals, 80-51, behind Laeticia Amihere's season-high off the bench and defensive block party.
